This topic describes how to install and configure Ops Manager before deploying <%= vars.product_full %> on Google Cloud Platform (GCP).

## <a id='prerequisites'></a>Prerequisites

You use Ops Manager to install and configure <%= vars.product_short %>.
Before you install Ops Manager, review [GCP Prerequisites and Resource Requirements](gcp-requirements.html).

## <a id="install-om"></a>Install and Configure Ops Manager

Each version of <%= vars.product_short %> is compatible with multiple versions of Ops Manager.
To determine Ops Manager compatibility,
see [<%= vars.product_network %>](https://network.pivotal.io/products/pivotal-container-service).

